text: Dorothy Hey (date of birth unknown, died 9 September 2015) was a British gymnast. She competed in the women's artistic team all-around at the 1948 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:Year of birth missing Category:2015 deaths Category:British female artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Great Britain Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Bradford
